description: The winding path leads from the sparse forest of the highlands to the east to the denser forest down to the west.  You can hear the playful sounds of a pair of bear cubs playing nearby.  You shudder a little and hope that the mamma bear is occupied elsewhere.

The winding path leads from the sparse forest of the highlands to the east to the denser forest down to the west.  In the dim moonlight you can make out several gashes on the nearby trees.  Apparently, this is bear territory.
title: [Lysierian Hills, Winding Path]
